<%- unless logged_in? -%>
  <%- title 'Welcome to document repository' -%>
  <div class="container-left-half-column">
    <dl>
      <dt><span>Recently updated</span></dt>
      <dd>
        <ul>
          <li><a href=""">User 1</a> / <a href=""">Document 1</a></li>
          <li><a href=""">User 2</a> / <a href=""">Document 2</a></li>
        </ul>
      </dd>
    </dl>
  </div>
  <div class="container-right-half-column">
    <p>With this service you can create documents using handy autofill function.</p>

    <p>Any registered user can create doc-template with "magic gaps", and then fill these gaps with wizard. <em>Anytime.</em></p>
    <p>Or any user can find doc-template in public repository, fork them and use later.</p>
  </div>
  <br class="clearboth" />
<%- else -%>
  <%- title current_user.email -%>
  <%= image_tag @user.gravatar_url %>

  <div class="common-container">
    <div class="container-left-half-column">
      <dl>
        <dt><span>Last updated templates</span></dt>
        <dd>
          <ul>
            <li>...</li>
          </ul>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      <p>
        <%= link_to 'Add new', new_user_template_path(current_user), :class => 'button' -%> or <%= link_to 'View all templates', user_templates_path(current_user) -%>
      </p>

      <dl>
        <dt><span>Your last documents</span></dt>
        <dd>
          <ul>
            <li>...</li>
          </ul>
        </dd>
      </dl>
      <p>
        <%= link_to 'View all templates', user_templates_path(current_user) -%>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-left-half-column">
      <h4>Following</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>...</li>
      </ul>
      <h4>News feed</h4>
      <p>List of activities of followed users.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>...</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <br class="clearboth" />
  </div>
<%- end -%>